{"tid":2405940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"譚德塞: 到訪武漢的專家下周將發表匯報","createTime":"2021-02-12T19:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T20:21:39.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"411afcada76e3dd29691a62f5b988282ca393bde","tid":2405940,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T19:18:31.000Z","msg":"世界衛生組織總幹事譚德塞透露，到訪武漢的專家下周將發表匯報。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞與到訪武漢的專家組組長巴瑞克會晤傳媒時重申，專家組在困難的環境下，進行非常重要的科學活動。他表示，現階段依然存在任何可能性，需要進一步分析及研究，重申添加專家組的重要資料後，更加接近對病毒源頭的理解。<br />\n<br />\n巴瑞克強調，排除實驗室洩漏病毒的可能性。他強調，專家組獲告知武漢細菌實驗室內初時並沒有工作人員管有新冠病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575492-20210213.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575492-20210213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FAxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=b608c766\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575492-20210213.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b187c35b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575492-20210213.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"df27b782c662fe8fb90293437eb67305fdc1439a","tid":2405940,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T19:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咸濕菜專用icon<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa52de9bd8f17751cc315f4f865a21ef344e89dc","tid":2405940,"uid":173060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"獲告知就係， ok u win<img src=\"/asset